<div class="expanded">
<h2 class="bac"><img class="pclose" src="../images/clear.gif">Our Business</h2>
<div>
<h3 class="bac">Summary</h3>
<ul class="bac">
	<li>Location: London</li>
	<li>12 month industrial placement programme starting in July</li>
	<li>On track for a minimum of a 2:1 degree classification (or equivalent) from a Computer Science or related discipline</li>
	<li>Genuine interest in a technology career within financial markets</li>
</ul>
<p class="bac">Innovation is at the heart of everything we do. Continuous improvement and a desire to remain at the forefront of the world&#39;s financial markets is what makes working at Bank&nbsp;of&nbsp;America Merrill Lynch such an exciting place.</p>
<p class="bac">Technology embraces everything from sales, trading and research applications, trade processing, risk management, portfolio management, payment services, voice recognition, and quantitative and qualitative analysis, to security analytics and relationship management.</p>
<p class="bac">We have an incredible global reach - we are spread across 35 different countries around the globe. We recognize the importance of technology and understand how it changes businesses and have become a home for some of the best minds in the field.</p>
<p class="bac">You could be part of a global team that delivers some of the most sophisticated financial technology systems in the world.</p>
<p class="bac">We invest in our technology and operations because we want to be the best - that is why we need the very best recruits.</p>
<p class="bac">We are looking for ambitious technology students to work with the latest technology and the smartest people at the heart of the financial world. And we mean world. The global nature of our technology function will allow you the opportunity to travel, work and interact with colleagues across the globe.</p>
</div></div>

<div class="expand">
<h2 class="bac"><img class="popen" src="../images/clear.gif">Overview</h2>
<div>
<p class="bac nobr">Life on the 12 month placement looks like this:</p>
<ul class="bac">
	<li>Assisting with designing, developing and deploying of state-of-the-art applications</li>
	<li>Bringing new ideas to the table and constantly seeking ways to do things better</li>
	<li>Analysis, testing and support of some our most complex technology platforms</li>
</ul>
</div></div>

<div class="expand">
<h2 class="bac"><img class="popen" src="../images/clear.gif">Training</h2>
<div>
<p class="bac nobr">We&#39;ll feed your appetite for learning through:</p>
<ul class="bac">
	<li>A one week training programme giving you the opportunity to learn more about the bank before being assigned to your team</li>
	<li>Senior Speaker Series during your first 2 months, featuring presentations by top executives</li>
	<li>Opportunities to interact with senior leaders and network with peers</li>
	<li>Constructive feedback sessions through performance evaluations</li>
	<li>Real involvement in key projects</li>
</ul>
</div></div>

<div class="expand">
<h2 class="bac"><img class="popen" src="../images/clear.gif">Qualifications</h2>
<div>
<p class="bac nobr">Bank&nbsp;of&nbsp;America Merrill Lynch is every bit as advanced, diverse and exciting as you&#39;d expect it to be, you&#39;re welcome to join us if you have:</p>
<ul class="bac">
	<li>A passion for Technology and desire to be part of a great team</li>
	<li>A working knowledge of programming languages such as Java and/or C++</li>
	<li>Degree subjects covering Computer Science, Mathematics, Physics and Engineering</li>
	<li>Analytical ability, communication and problem solving skills</li>
</ul>
</div></div>

